title: A Guide to the Project Management Body of Knowledge (Pmbok Guide
description:
A reflection on the collaboration and knowledge of working
project managers that provides the fundamentals of project
management as they apply to a wide range of projects. This
internationally recognized standard provides the essential
tools to practice project management and
deliver organizational results. 

A Guide to the Project Management Body of Knowledge
(Pmbok Guide) - 5th Edition
By: Project Management Institute
Format: PDF
Language: EN
Pages: 616
ISBN: 9781935589679
